      • idToString

        public static String idToString(long id)
        Converts a long job or execution ID to a string representation. Currently it is an unsigned 16-digit hex number.

      • idFromString

        public static long idFromString(String str)
        Parses the jobId formatted with idToString(long).

        The method is lenient: if the string doesn't match the structure output by idToString or if the string is null, it will return -1.

        Returns:
        the parsed ID or -1 if parsing failed.

      • toCompletableFuture

        public static <T> CompletableFuture<T> toCompletableFuture(ICompletableFuture<T> future)
        Wraps Hazelcast IMDG's ICompletableFuture into Java's standard CompletableFuture.
        Parameters:
        future - the future to wrap
        Returns:
        a new CompletableFuture wrapping the given one
